            "heading": "About the role",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "template--18850231484751__f5332588-ee9e-4cb8-b588-7497ef23f2f0-16824067253affbd63-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This year, Loop was awarded the fastest growing Belgian scale-up by Deloitte. By the end of 2022, we will be 120 Loopers and next year we'll double the current team once again. The Talent Acquisition Manager will play a key role in finding and attracting the excellent A-players we need to ensure the future growth of the company.<br\/><br\/>You will be entrusted with an ongoing quest to discover top talent, by adapting our value proposition to what is important for our audiences. You'll ensure great relationships with both candidates and hiring manager. We expect you to be experienced in full-cycle recruiting, direct sourcing and in managing a recruitment team. You should have a sharp eye for talented people and a steady commitment to help them find success in our company.<\/p>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "c1f503b4-5a46-4990-8e45-753347835b3c",
